      • isOnline

        public final java.lang.String isOnline()
        Gets the online status flag of either 'Y', 'N' or '' if this is not a status request message.
        Returns:
        String of the flag value of the message. If the message is not a status request the result will be an empty string, otherwise the result could be either 'Y' or 'N'.
